latestPosts.caption:
The Ultimate StarMaker✨🧿♥️
.
.
Pappaaa, I can’t thank you enough for what you did for me! I remember during covid times i used to sit in a room from the dusk till night doing makeup on myself, i noticed that you were also sitting in the next room waiting for me to complete the look just to compliment my hardwork and telling my mistakes that i should work on! I will never forget the confidence you had when i started my journey! I will never forget the fact that you had faith in me when i almost gave up! I will never forget that face when you dropped me off in delhi for my further makeup study. I will never forget the smile on your face when i came back to you after months! Just like that I WILL NEVER FORGET TO MAKE YOU PROUDER ♥️🧿
Love you the coolest father of all time🤍✨💎
PAPPA: The reason I’m the strongest, the reason I’m BS now✨♥️
